snippet.title: Blood Typers | Official Announcement Teaser Trailer
snippet.description:
TYPE TO KILL in this survival horror adventure. 
https://store.steampowered.com/app/2790330/Blood_Typers/
Alone or with friends, explore a sprawling cursed film studio as its horror movies bleed into reality. Choose from a roster of characters then plan your escape from this bloody homage to old school horror. But remember... death is just a typo away.
